long_description: with a large selection of rental, retail, and custom clothing options we are confident you will find exactly what you're looking for. our store atmosphere is warm, inviting, and there is a reason why customers travel the state to come to cardita, it's the experience. clifford has been in the formal wear industry for 30 years, and after corporate downsizing in 2007, we decided to open our own business, cardita. we had a dream, offering a unique, first-class experience that was lacking in the market and developing a brand synonymous with quality and fashion. clifford, a third-generation clothier, and victoria, a fashion and interior designer, and when the two are blended, you have cardita. our brand continues to grow adding services such as concierge services, cigar shop, and custom clothing. made in one size yours . custom clothing. from custom jeans made in italy to handsome sweaters from bugatti. we have the styles and fashions you're looking for. don't wait they will be gone!facts: all these items are individual exchanges on rental tuxedos for weddings today.
